<div class="form-flexbox-lhs">
  <div class="half-page-wider">
    <h2 class="two-color-headline">group<span class="nest-purple">placement</span></h2>
    <p>Based on your profile we can determine the best 3 group options for you to join. The following parent groups are recommended to you because the members are based in your general area and, importantly, the due dates / birth dates of their babies align with yours â€“ an important factor for peer support, understanding and relating to one another.</p>

    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
      <% @relevant_groups.each do |group| %>
        <div class="group-rec-card">
          <%= image_tag asset_path("tree-thumbnail.png"), class: "tn-avatar-lg-purple" %>
          <h2><%= group.name.downcase %></h2>
          <h6><%= group.post_code %></h6>
          <% if current_user.groups.include?(group) %>
            <p>You're already<br>a part of<br>this group</p>
          <% else %>
            <%= button_to "join", join_group_path(group), class: "card-link" %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <p>A supportive space where you can share advice, moral support, and laughter is within reach.</p>
    <p>Otherwise, you can start your very own group <%= link_to "here", new_group_path %></p>
    <p>Not interested in joining a togthernest community group today? Click <%= link_to "here", root_path %></p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tree-bg-group-rec"></div>
